headline: JPMorgan: $34bn Base token, waning DEX threat, could boost Coinbase stock
summary: A Base token could have a market value at high as $34 billion, according to JPMorgan analysts. They also see Coinbase benefiting from better monetisation of USDC rewards and from the waning threat of decentralised exchanges.
